== Changelog ==
= 2.4.5 =
* Added missing translation strings

= 2.4.4 =
* Fixed image stretching in old versions of Internet Explorer

= 2.4.3 =
* Fixed some bugs in the attachment template

= 2.4.2 =
* Added attachment template for post attachments
* Fixed admin comments - now admin comments will display an asterisk

= 2.4.1 =
* Fixed images being squished on the full-width page template

= 2.4 =
* Fixed maximum widths for images & other media
* Changed admin styles to match WordPress defaults
* Accessibility improvements on search form
* Added styles to captions
* CSS selector cleanup

= 2.3 =
* Replaced the old logo uploader with a faster version that uses WP core.
* Add a check_hash function to validate hex color output and add # if missing.
* Add a check for border_color values.